This script will add tracks to ~/CurrentCD.m3u.  When size >= 700MB, will try to burn an mp3 CD, and clear the playlist.

In KDE: System Settings > Shortcuts and Gestures > Edit > New > Global Shortcut > Command:
        Trigger Tab: Set shortcut to whatever key combo you wish.
        Action Tab: Set action to: python $HOME/bin/amarok2m3u.py (or wherever you put this script).

Requires (All available in Debian):
    Amarok
    KDE
    genisoimage
    wodim
    notify-send
